metadata.name: Nebula
metadata.description:
“Nebula” is a generative project programmed in Touch Designer software to recreate 90,000 Galaxies through creative coding and random patterns.

It aims to represent how Galaxies are born and then merge into bigger Clusters. This project is in live rendering.

The buyer of this NFT will receive a .toe file, where the central Galaxy is located in the form of live rendering, you can navigate through the central Galaxy, replace the Galaxy’s color, and adjust the output resolution.

The buyer will also receive the Full HQ Version (1920*1080 resolution, 30 FPS, 1:08 length).
